    <h1><?= $escaper->escapeHtml(__('Panth Search Autocomplete — Documentation')) ?></h1>
    <p>An engine-agnostic, bot-hardened, cached search autocomplete for Hyva and Luma. Searches products, categories, and CMS pages in real time using whichever search backend the merchant has configured (Elasticsearch 7, Elasticsearch 8, OpenSearch, or MySQL fallback) — the same code path runs on every supported Magento install.</p>

